ocation":2,"to":444.5},{"content":"那根线是我与父亲麒麟丸之间","from":445.68,"location":2,"to":448.38},{"content":"持续了六百年的孽缘","from":448.38,"location":2,"to":450.39},{"content":"请您帮我斩断它吧","from":450.95,"location":2,"to":452.58},{"content":"虽然我还没尝试过这样做","from":454.23,"location":2,"to":455.58},{"content":"这样我一定能前往彼世","from":456.65,"location":2,"to":460.09},{"content":"欸 你会死吗","from":461.84,"location":2,"to":463.57},{"content":"我早就死了","from":463.91,"location":2,"to":465.76},{"content":"拜托了 这样一定能阻止麒麟丸的横暴专行","from":466.32,"location":2,"to":471.94},{"content":"明白了","from":473.87,"location":2,"to":474.85},{"content":"如果斩不断这个","from":489.91,"location":2,"to":491.03},{"content":"那是露与母亲之间的缘 想必也无法斩断了","from":491.64,"location":2,"to":494.55},{"content":"是死是活 只有先试试了","from":496.89,"location":2,"to":500.07},{"content":"幻梦蝴蝶！","from":511.09,"location":2,"to":512.13},{"content":"抱歉 我好像砍错了","from":515.35,"location":2,"to":517.62},{"content":"不","from":517.99,"location":2,"to":518.6},{"content":"难道这是刹那的蝴蝶吗","from":519.03,"location":2,"to":521.36},{"content":"这是我的蝴蝶","from":521.63,"location":2,"to":524.04},{"content":"这是麒麟丸将我束缚在此地的缘","from":525.93,"location":2,"to":530.12},{"content":"璃苑 你难道对这份父爱感到厌倦了吗","from":532.71,"location":2,"to":536.48},{"content":"是因为我还没有将它运用自如吗","from":539.07,"location":2,"to":542.04},{"content":"茧…坏掉了","from":544.9,"location":2,"to":547.37},{"content":"这是什么","from":548.3,"location":2,"to":549.24},{"content":"是用我的骨灰与坟土制成的灵魂容器","from":549.7,"location":2,"to":554.11},{"content":"六百年间你一直被困在这里吗","from":554.75,"location":2,"to":558.12},{"content":"是的","from":559.02,"location":2,"to":559.54},{"content":"璃苑 璃苑","from":566.51,"location":2,"to":568.76},{"content":"外面很危险 老老实实地回到茧里","from":569.6,"location":2,"to":573.8},{"content":"不可以去产灵山外面","from":574.79,"location":2,"to":576.55},{"content":"又强行把她扯回去了","from":582.54,"location":2,"to":584.32},{"content":"璃苑！","from":584.54,"location":2,"to":585.23},{"content":"我已经成功逃离了你的束缚","from":585.88,"location":2,"to":590.01},{"content":"我会行动 我现